The,eXactmobile,service,allows,businesses,to,set,up,and,manage,their,own,SMS,messaging,campaigns,After,signing,up,the,business,selects,an,administrator,to,add,new,users,manage,accounts,etc,The,business,users,can,then,use,the,eXactmobile,website,to,type,out,a,message,or,import,one,if,preferred,and,send,it,to,the,target,groups,or,individuals,eXactmobile,users,can,set,up,a,database,of,mobile,numbers,that,can,then,be,accessed,and,manipulated,to,simplify,messaging,eXactmobile,s,messaging,functions,can,also,be,invoked,using,its,SOAP,based,API,allowing,them,to,be,integrated,into,other,applications